    SETTINGS -->|окна| PENDING

    MARK --> RECORD
    PENDING -->|deadline| FAILED
    FAILED --> PENALTY
    FAILED --> PUSH2
    FAILED --> PUSH3
    GPS_BG --> PUSH1

    style ATTENDANCE fill:#11998e,color:#fff
    style MARK fill:#38ef7d,color:#000
    style PENDING fill:#FFC107,color:#000
    style FAILED fill:#f44336,color:#fff
```

